# React Cohort Tracker

## Description

This project demonstrates styling React components using CSS Modules and inline styles. It displays cohort details with different styles based on the cohort status.

## Technologies Used

- React
- JavaScript (ES6)
- CSS Modules
- HTML
- Node.js
- npm

## Features

- CSS Modules
- Inline Styling
- Dynamic Styling
- Styled React Components
- Cohort Details Dashboard

## Project Structure

```
cohorttracker
│
├── src
│   ├── Components
│   │   └── CohortDetails.js
│   ├── CohortDetails.module.css
│   ├── App.js
│   └── index.js
```

## Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/cohorttracker.git
cd cohorttracker
npm install
npm start
```

## Learning Outcomes

- CSS Modules
- Inline Styles
- Dynamic Component Styling
- React Component Design
- className and style Properties
